{"tid":867493,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"只厚 5.9 毫米！Apple 本年度全新 iPad Pro 設計規格釋出","createTime":"2018-10-18T16:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T08:37:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"02eca8a799ef68e462903830033382df2bbe2002","tid":867493,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T16:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Iiz06tWHORhmmg7H92BQvQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/c470b65ef39e83f4d65b66b80d54ea37\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIiz06tWHORhmmg7H92BQvQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fc470b65ef39e83f4d65b66b80d54ea37&h=92577fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本周一大重點，相信便是各位終於可以預購 iPhone XR，擁有稱為 Liquid Retina Display，6.1&rdquo; 最先進 LCD 屏幕，達至 1792 x 828，326 ppi，具有 IP67 防塵和防液體保護，前方依然保留如 iPhone X 一樣的 TrueDepth 系統及移除 Home 鍵。而 Apple 亦將為 iPhone XR 推出全新透明保護殻，以彰顯其背部的六種色彩。與此同時，稍早便有消息預測本年度全新 iPad Pro 將更新多項細節，更預計這個月將會迎來一個小型發佈。而據網民及一些網站透露，以及 Slashleaks 不久前分享的設計規格，顯示出新款 iPad Pro 將會是歷來最薄設備之一。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TDRmZMdBE.9eCxTiTnNYpQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/7b7e568a0ab895370b591f1f649da77b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTDRmZMdBE.9eCxTiTnNYpQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F7b7e568a0ab895370b591f1f649da77b&h=a313217d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有關設計圖也符合當前 iPad Pro 的測量，不過便是因為機身薄了，才能「順理成章」的將 3.5mm 耳機孔捨棄。而大尺寸為 280.66 x 215 毫米，小的則是 247.64 x 178.52 毫米，兩款將只厚 5.9 毫米。而加上先前預測細節，如擁有將近無邊框設計，捨棄 Home 按鈕，換上 Face ID 作為解鎖功能，及因為邊框足夠容納 Face ID 所需的 TrueDepth 相機系統而不會有「M額」設計。那到底還將有甚麼新增功能值得期待呢？不妨期待着 Apple 的發佈到來，以及繼續留意我們 HYPEBEAST 的跟進報導。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image-cdn.hypb.st/https%3A%2F%2Fhk.hypebeast.com%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F10%2Fapple-event-new-york-city01.jpg?q=90&amp;w=1400&amp;cbr=1&amp;fit=max\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage-cdn.hypb.st%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fhk.hypebeast.com%252Ffiles%252F2018%252F10%252Fapple-event-new-york-city01.jpg%3Fq%3D90%26w%3D1400%26cbr%3D1%26fit%3Dmax&h=fb12fdec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66618fec234ba74f9d649b6ada54e9403b876553","tid":867493,"uid":51920,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:14:58.000Z","msg":"買黎睇av 一流"},{"pid":"54b405aaa94a68f396b649f7808da71764e81afe","tid":867493,"uid":75193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T19:28:58.000Z","msg":"薄好 不過唔好整細舊電"},{"pid":"a4b4bf714f21270040a1bf67b0965c3b057e8dbf","tid":867493,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66618fec234ba74f9d649b6ada54e9403b876553","tid":867493,"uid":51920,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:14:58.000Z","msg":"買黎睇av 一流"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T19:34:25.000Z","msg":"ios隨時可以上埋app store下載埋dmm apps <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369e6cd5c38134bb61e8acd27148e5920873b757","tid":867493,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T00:41:49.000Z","msg":"擁有稱為 Liquid Retina Display，6.1&rdquo; 最先進 LCD 屏幕，達至 1792 x 828，326 ppi<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31db4363e92ea33a3e86801c992c6ffc69dcf02","tid":867493,"uid":18167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"369e6cd5c38134bb61e8acd27148e5920873b757","tid":867493,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T00:41:49.000Z","msg":"擁有稱為 Liquid Retina Display，6.1&rdquo; 最先進 LCD 屏幕，達至 1792 x 828，326 ppi<br />\n<br />\n<br />